modName: Cutting Room Floor and Whiterun Outskirts Market Compatibility Patch
summary: This is a small compatibility patch for Arthmoor's Cutting Room Floor and RadioBoX's Whiterun Outskirts Market.
descriptionHtml:
This is a small compatibility patch for Arthmoor's Cutting Room Floor and RadioBoX's Whiterun Outskirts Market.


THIS MOD REQUIRES:

Unofficial Skyrim Patch:
Cutting Room Floor:
Whiterun Outskirts Market:


Installation:

Download and activate with NMM
or
Extract the .esp to your Skyrim data folder --> Steam/Steamapps/common/Skyrim/Data


Recommended Mods:

As this is dealing with the Whiterun area I am going to sugest some of my favorite mods in the area.

Dawn of Whiterun by BluePianoTwo http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37460/
aMidianBorn Whiterun by CaBaL http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38491/
Elysium Estate bythejadeshadow http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33939/ -- My preferred house mod.
author: lworm17
